Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.38,0:02:12.85,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)\an8\fs21\be1}第七回  「信奈上洛」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.77,0:02:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁戴將軍上洛的計劃泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍雖然被暗殺了  但是還有弟弟義昭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.92,0:02:23.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把義昭奉為新的將軍的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.57,0:02:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就有上洛的大義名分了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.52,0:02:29.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰被暗殺了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.89,0:02:32.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了是將軍足利義輝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:34.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義輝公沒有被暗殺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.16,0:02:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.82,0:02:38.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且不是弟弟  是妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.41,0:02:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等  等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.28,0:02:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲的事件應該是將軍被暗殺…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.55,0:02:46.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將軍在千鈞一髮之際逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.18,0:02:50.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和妹妹義昭大人一起逃往大陸了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.11,0:02:52.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.57,0:02:57.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歷史要是走向我不知道的岔路的話
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.43,0:02:59.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的存在價值就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.46,0:03:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猴子要從樹上掉下來咯  猴子前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.67,0:03:08.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我來代替連猴子的智慧都沒有了的相良前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.82,0:03:11.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發表一個好提案
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:15.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被織田家抓住的今川義元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.82,0:03:17.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有足利家的血脈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:20.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有繼承將軍家的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.86,0:03:25.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把今川義元奉為下一任將軍上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.08,0:03:33.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  不枉我讓你加入織田家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.75,0:03:35.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追上相良前輩並超越他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:38.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.53,0:03:42.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼織田軍開始上洛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.72,0:03:43.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.04,0:03:51.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,途中有淺井和六角等強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:52.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也真夠纏人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.51,0:04:03.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田和淺井應該結盟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想和淺井為敵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.42,0:04:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係啊  為敵又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我完全不怕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.20,0:04:15.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  怕的是你那邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.78,0:04:18.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟到處宣揚要結婚了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.25,0:04:21.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是在這裡被取消婚事的話就成天下人的笑柄了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.13,0:04:23.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.04,0:04:27.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過呢  你要是哭著求我  也許可以考慮一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:29.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:31.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  這事就當沒發生過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.87,0:04:37.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不能結婚的話  我就回不去了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.67,0:04:39.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當幫幫我  請一定…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:41.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.21,0:04:45.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的妹妹嫁給你好了  感謝我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.72,0:04:46.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有聽說過信奈大人有妹妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:53.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…有啦  說有就有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是再囉嗦就取消婚事咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.50,0:04:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跪求您妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.33,0:05:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  信長也有個妹妹的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.70,0:05:07.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕世美女  阿市！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.89,0:05:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐  姐姐大人…這究竟是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.21,0:05:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你嫁出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:19.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始你就是淺井長政的夫人了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:20.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夫人？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.32,0:05:23.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你們幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:27.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.40,0:05:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.16,0:05:30.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是欺詐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:33.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不被發現就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.78,0:05:36.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你可糊弄不了我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.26,0:05:36.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們約好了打下美濃就給我美少女作為獎勵的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.55,0:05:43.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不給我的話  我就不幹活咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.91,0:05:47.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我美少女啦  美少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:52.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求我這麼無聊的事情  你真不要臉啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.19,0:05:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少廢話！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.31,0:05:58.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人拼命的理由  只有那個吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:00.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:03.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守約定的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.26,0:06:11.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚洗乾淨給我等著
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.54,0:06:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰呢  是誰呢～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:26.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我的胸部…那麼好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向姐姐撒嬌  給100分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:39.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前輩  請對我溫柔點哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每個都很讚！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.54,0:06:48.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這裡果然應該是要高嶺之花…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.81,0:06:49.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義元妹妹！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.64,0:06:56.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難  難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.60,0:06:57.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會是信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.66,0:06:59.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.28,0:07:01.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她根本就對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.36,0:07:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  不過…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…為什麼我要給猴子糟蹋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.80,0:07:14.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要滿懷感激地  接受獎勵哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.48,0:07:17.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是天下第一的美少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟  糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.74,0:07:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心  心理準備還…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.71,0:07:28.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,公主大人說要獎勵你  猴子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.62,0:07:35.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天下第一的美少女  寧寧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天開始就來當猴子大人的妹妹吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.48,0:07:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高興吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.95,0:07:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那傢伙…！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.40,0:07:48.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欺詐啊——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.34,0:07:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和淺井長政結盟的信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.18,0:07:58.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始向南近江進軍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了六角承禎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.97,0:08:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼近了京都
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.79,0:08:17.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了這個陣容  京都就近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.62,0:08:19.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:34.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來看看京都裡的美女  結果完全變成荒涼之地了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  來人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.46,0:08:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.96,0:08:43.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大白天的就入室搶劫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是三好軍的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.84,0:08:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他們嗎  怎麼看都像山賊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滾開滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.12,0:08:53.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為幕府倒臺了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:56.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都已經成了無法之地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:08:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈讓我們來打探是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.22,0:09:00.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是想確認今天的日本中心…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:05.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去了統治者的國家的樣子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:07.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.62,0:09:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和五右衛門先去收集情報
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.01,0:09:16.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生你們請去姬巫女大人所在的大和御所看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.62,0:09:17.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:22.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人是站在大和的頂點的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說是創建這個國家的諸神的子孫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人崇拜供奉著
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我所在的世界  似乎有微妙的不同啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.29,0:09:40.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.50,0:09:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次別想逃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:49.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧  沒受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.66,0:09:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這孩子有一種不可思議的氣質呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.65,0:09:57.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.39,0:09:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.52,0:10:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是離開這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.94,0:10:15.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.28,0:10:18.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然敢去襲擊御所
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.80,0:10:20.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會輕易放過你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.76,0:10:23.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關白  近衛前久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.37,0:10:28.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在暗中操縱公家和政治的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.44,0:10:30.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉  
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.32,0:10:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些鼠輩已經被砍頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.80,0:10:37.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下賤者的人頭誰要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬巫女大人到底去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.07,0:10:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虧你們還是三好三人眾  這可不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.59,0:10:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堺之豪商  津田宗及
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.58,0:10:51.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是為了錢什麼都肯做的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.54,0:10:54.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易打倒了將軍
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.91,0:10:57.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這種事  連一文都沒賺到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.12,0:11:00.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨敵退散  南蠻覆滅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.42,0:11:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統領比叡山的正覺院豪盛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把南蠻人當作仇敵的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:12.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要從南蠻人手裡保護這個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.16,0:11:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須由我們來掌權
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們必須要有姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.14,0:11:20.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  近衛大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.80,0:11:23.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  你肯出面了啊  彈正
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永彈正久秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.00,0:11:32.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫不在乎地反覆倒戈和謀反
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.81,0:11:34.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是戰國的魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.59,0:11:40.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們來說姬巫女大人是重要的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.63,0:11:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,箕作城也攻下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:48.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀態不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.86,0:11:51.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然想到對所有的城池進行同時攻擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:54.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角一定嚇呆了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.89,0:11:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們這裡有很多優秀的武將嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有空跟他一點點耗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.96,0:12:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可以說是妙策  95分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.42,0:12:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相良前輩  現在一定為立不了功而不爽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.27,0:12:11.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  京都那邊比較重要
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.47,0:12:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來似乎很混亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.27,0:12:16.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在擔心嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.11,0:12:19.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半兵衛和五右衛門也在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.87,0:12:22.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒  沒問題的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.16,0:12:27.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點  解決掉六角去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.11,0:12:44.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.16,0:12:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.02,0:12:53.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真無法想像這裡就是京都
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.70,0:12:56.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的世界不是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.35,0:13:00.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要靠近我  卑賤之徒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.98,0:13:03.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們嘗嘗必殺奧義
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.78,0:13:08.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸亦當如此強力劍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.76,0:13:11.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  西洋修女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:20.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,金髮和巨乳的組合  破壞力太強了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.68,0:13:22.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真差勁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛苦是不能通過暴力治癒的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:30.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起祈禱吧  給予你的敵人愛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.14,0:13:34.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就來好好地愛一下你的敵人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.18,0:13:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿  我還是第一次騎大洋馬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.00,0:13:48.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身為日本之民  要知道羞恥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼給我滾開
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.47,0:14:00.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯嘛  我梵天丸也不會輸給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:15.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找～到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.60,0:14:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是葡萄牙來的傳教士
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.74,0:14:26.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲·弗洛伊斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.61,0:14:28.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是相良良晴
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.72,0:14:29.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,犬千代
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.87,0:14:31.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是破壞的大魔王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,默示錄裡的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梵天丸是也
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.01,0:14:40.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.47,0:14:41.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你們真不走運呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.21,0:14:43.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來京都傳教的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.04,0:14:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平時我都在堺的南蠻寺裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:52.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想來朝廷請求在全國傳教的許可
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.51,0:14:54.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不過被拒絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被拒絕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.83,0:15:01.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  他們說西洋人不能靠近御所
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.80,0:15:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真過分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:06.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很想見見姬巫女大人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.07,0:15:08.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.53,0:15:12.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想同樣是侍奉神的姬巫女大人的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.49,0:15:14.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許會理解我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.21,0:15:16.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終結戰亂之世
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:20.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓國家變得安居樂業
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.70,0:15:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是神的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  那也是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.28,0:15:29.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想會實現的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.59,0:15:32.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴先生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.33,0:15:35.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢想只要不放棄就會實現
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然會讓人感覺很幼稚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.08,0:15:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我是對此深信不疑的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我也相信
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.41,0:15:48.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的只有觀音寺城了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.44,0:15:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一口氣攻下它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.54,0:15:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  還是勸他們來投降吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.43,0:15:56.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不認為他們會答應的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意投降的話  就放他們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.29,0:16:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必去追
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.03,0:16:02.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是讓他們逃跑嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.43,0:16:04.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.95,0:16:08.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是符合公主殿下的風格啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:10.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事根本是聞所未聞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.42,0:16:13.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要我們能成功上洛就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有必要做出無謂的流血犧牲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.28,0:16:20.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角那個蠢貨
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.74,0:16:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是戰至最後一人  拖住織田信奈就好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:30.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六角大人會不會逃到甲賀的深山裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.98,0:16:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎麼淒慘也該有個限度吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.58,0:16:37.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,統治著越前的朝倉義景
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是被稱作名門的大大名
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.93,0:16:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然讓傻瓜公主上洛  這世道也算走到頭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:52.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡將今川義元那樣的鄉下大名輔佐為將軍  才是原本的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.39,0:16:53.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,義元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.29,0:16:59.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何也要得到那位公主  並添加到余的作品中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:02.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的興趣還真是沒變啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.69,0:17:09.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不知道是哪裡的笨蛋讓足利將軍的妹妹逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想愚弄我們嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:16.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要是有意見的話  就把越前七十五萬石的朝倉當作對手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.79,0:17:20.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,內訌可沒有任何好處啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:22.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:26.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三好和朝倉  再加上武田和上杉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:29.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能形成信奈包圍網了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是完成這個是需要花時間的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.70,0:17:35.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈上洛的速度應該更快吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.22,0:17:41.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暫且先撤兵  在京都周圍燃起大火
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:46.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈花時間滅火的話  余的士兵和武田、上杉家就能趕過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.40,0:17:50.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼就交給你們了  三好三人眾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:52.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要…要由我們來迎擊嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.46,0:17:54.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有松永彈正
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:58.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全軍要拼死與信奈戰鬥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.62,0:17:59.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.49,0:18:02.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,余也會伸出援手的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:08.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對信奈恨之入骨的男人  也來助一臂之力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.33,0:18:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是快點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:28.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是京都最糟糕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.23,0:18:31.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想親眼看一看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.29,0:18:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.26,0:18:40.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論百姓如何悲歎痛苦  不出來看一看是不知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.23,0:18:47.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先暫且不說未來  這個地獄是現在真實存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:51.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  她知道我是來自未來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:56.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百姓們能夠歡聲笑語的世界會來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:02.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.17,0:19:04.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何能夠斷言？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有織田信奈在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.19,0:19:11.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈奪取天下之後  會創造一個嶄新的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.32,0:19:12.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織田信奈？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.59,0:19:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.43,0:19:18.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都歡笑著  和弗洛伊斯姐姐一樣的西洋人做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何人都能和平生活的世界  信奈一定能創造出來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是信奈的夢想嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.25,0:19:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信奈的夢想也是大家的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.64,0:19:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  只要不放棄的話  夢想終會成真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:35.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.79,0:19:36.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.79,0:19:40.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.34,0:19:49.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭…頭有點暈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:04.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松永彈正  前來迎接您
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.93,0:20:06.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來帶我回去的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.82,0:20:12.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就當作是你被無禮之徒強行帶著到處跑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:15.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准對他們動手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.71,0:20:19.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我老老實實跟你回去  這樣就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.98,0:20:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.65,0:20:37.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是什麼啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於找到你了  相良氏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.30,0:20:43.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五右衛門  半兵衛妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:49.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個氣息…是被鬼魂什麼的襲擊了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.22,0:20:51.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.54,0:20:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:55.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.52,0:21:01.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的送到這裡就行了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝你幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.13,0:21:11.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個不可思議的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.93,0:21:13.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是住在這裡的巫女嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.70,0:21:19.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,良晴  這次玩得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕由衷地表示感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.90,0:21:25.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朕？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姬…巫女殿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.57,0:21:35.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是  織田信奈終於完成了上洛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.68,0:21:40.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,京都成為織田家所統治的區域
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.67,0:21:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照你說的  我讓京都的治安恢復正常了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.85,0:21:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像相當嚴重呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:52.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣應該就會好一些了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.76,0:21:53.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.87,0:21:55.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是做了應該做的事而已
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.30,0:21:59.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕的地方還有很多很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.52,0:22:01.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是我奪取天下之前罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.77,0:22:07.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  信奈
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.00,0:22:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.90,0:22:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造一個和平的國家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.94,0:22:16.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,====================================
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:35.54,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ただ  時代の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:40.92,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}立たされて  戸惑う時に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:46.36,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}手を引いてくれた人へ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.59,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}出来ること探した
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.02,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}傷つきながら  笑う姿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.21,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}心の裏  涙が見えた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:06.60,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}救い求める声  聴き取れるのは
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}許された者だけ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.97,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}数え切れぬ  嵐を越えて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:23.56,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの闇  裂くヒカリになる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.72,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もう  迷わない  ともに生きたい
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:34.15,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誓う夢が  どんな無謀であっても
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:43.95,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おぼえていて  信じられる場所は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:47.65,edj,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ここにあると
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.43,0:22:35.54,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只是深陷時代紛爭的漩渦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.77,0:22:40.92,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無奈佇立  獨自彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:46.36,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}一直在尋覓著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.50,0:22:50.59,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生命中不可或缺的那個他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.82,0:22:56.02,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}堅韌的外表  寂寞的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.17,0:23:01.21,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}掩藏不住內心幽然淚下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:06.60,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}彷彿能聆聽到救贖之音的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:12.70,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有尋覓著的他
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.20,0:23:17.97,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}經歷風花雪月的洗禮
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.08,0:23:23.56,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}方知孤影的你似流光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.69,0:23:28.72,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不再猶豫  願與你同存
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.85,0:23:34.15,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就算誓言之夢的前方是一片迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:43.95,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}請記住  屬於你的歸宿
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.09,0:23:47.65,edc,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就在此處
